<td align="center"><b>
<i>Eucera atriventris</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">&#40;Smith, 1854&#41;</font></b><br>
<small><i>Melissodes atriventris </i>Smith, 1854; <i>Synhalonia atriventris </i>&#40;Smith, 1854&#41;; <i>Synhalonia atriventris form </i>fuscipes_homonym Robertson, 1900; <i>Tetralonia robertsoni </i>Cockerell, 1914, replacement name; <i>Tetralonia atriventris </i>&#40;Smith, 1854&#41;</small><p>
